<p>
  <span class="nym">Richild</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Old High German</span> <i>rih</i> 'ruler' + <span class="lang">Old High German</span> <i>hiltja</i> 'battle'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a 9th C empress consort of the Franks, an 11th C queen of Hungary, a 12th C queen of Castile, and a 13th C queen of Norway.</p>
</div>
  
  
  


